<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2944911>
    dc:description "FIGURES 121–131. Ingrischgryllacris n. gen. 121–129. I. brevifalcatus carnapi n. comb. 121–122. Habitus lateral and dorsal. 123. Frons. 124. Head and pronotum in lateral view. 125. Hind femur. 126–129. Male terminalia in axial and lateral view. 130–131. I. brevifalcatus brevifalcatus. Habitus and ovipositor respectively. Photos by Sigfrid Ingrisch." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2944911/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

